Vampiric Cape by Accessories begins here.

A vampiric cape is a kind of neckwear. There is 1 unique vampiric cape. Printed name of vampiric cape is "[TQlink of item described][clothing-title-before]vampiric cape[clothing-title-after][TQxlink of item described][verb-desc of item described]". The text-shortcut of vampiric cape is "vc".

Figure of vampiric cape is the file "Items\Accessories\Neck\vampiriccape1.png".

To decide which figure-name is clothing-image of (C - a vampiric cape):
	decide on figure of vampiric cape.

To say ClothingDesc of (C - a vampiric cape):
	say "A black cape with a red inner lining[if C is worn]. It drapes down your back and sways with your every move[end if].".

To say ShortDesc of (C - a vampiric cape):
	say "vampiric cape".

To decide which number is the initial outrage of (C - a vampiric cape):
	decide on 1.
	
To decide which number is the dexterity-influence of (C - a vampiric cape):
	let X be 2;
	increase X by the magic-modifier of C;
	decide on X.

Vampiric Cape ends here.

